  "texts": [
    "WebMainBench is constructed using a hybrid sampling strategy to ensure both broad representation and relevance.",
    "90% of the samples are randomly drawn from the Common Crawl dataset to cover the long-tail web, while the remaining 10% are sampled from a list of top-ranking websites (Chinaz Alexafoot_3) to include popular, professionally designed pages.",
    "The final benchmark is highly diverse, containing pages from 5,434 unique top-level and 5,904 unique second-level domains.Annotation Rules.",
    "To address the ambiguity in defining \"main content\" for unconventional layouts, we establish two core annotation principles.",
    "First, Contextual Integrity dictates that content integral to the main article-such as a table of contents, abstract, or reference list-is included."
  ],
